name: Learning to see - True Colours v2
description: Memo Akten (memo.tv), 2017-2020. Part of the "Learning to see" series, learningtosee.ai. This particular incarnation was made in 2020 for Valentines Day, and minted April 2021 for #TheFen on H=N <3. An artificial neural network looks out onto the world, and tries to make sense of what it is seeing. But it can only see through the filter of what it already knows. Just like us. Because we too, see things not as they are, but as we are. I see your True Colours shining through...
